The paper discusses a machine learning algorithm for time series forecasting, which is a common topic in the machine learning community. The use of RNNs and state space models suggests that the paper may fall under the categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The focus on improving the speed and accessibility of the algorithm suggests that it may also fall under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) or cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the use of neural networks and optimization techniques suggests that it may also fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
